{"tid":2198634,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"周浩鼎促律政司徹查檢控主任涉鼓吹參與六四晚會","createTime":"2020-09-11T13:15:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-11T15:41:23.000Z","uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"7416333aeb064e5e4d74dfb5e8196c3ef61552f1","tid":2198634,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T13:15:31.000Z","msg":"有報道指現為東區法院高級二等檢控主任黃華芬，今年6.4以律政司內部電郵系統發電郵給全體檢控主任，慫恿其他檢控主任參與當晚六四悼念晚會。民建聯周浩鼎今日（11日）指，若報道屬實，將嚴重損害律政司檢控人員聲譽，又稱檢控人員涉嫌鼓吹他人參與非法集會令人感覺荒謬，要求律政司徹查事件。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200911/NWEE3RTZARHF3K24FHTFRW7AMI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200911%2FNWEE3RTZARHF3K24FHTFRW7AMI%2F&d=lPOaXpfFeUboYNX3auI3foCLuBk19a2msHWYQfvuVO4%3D&h=52f49a80\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200911%2FNWEE3RTZARHF3K24FHTFRW7AMI%2F&h=36a64f11\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200911/NWEE3RTZARHF3K24FHTFRW7AMI/</a>"},{"pid":"4d459dbcba0904e8d2bba05214146196257801ff","tid":2198634,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T13:22:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e6b14217ad812bfc95789b6afc046e57096b604","tid":2198634,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4d459dbcba0904e8d2bba05214146196257801ff","tid":2198634,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T13:22:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /